OL,7,FEx-broadcaster Huw Edwards "snubbed"
OL,8,FDavid Dimbleby during lunch, says
OL,9,Fformer Downing Street PR Chief, Guto
OL,10,FHarri.
OL,12,FHarri and Edwards worked together at
OL,13,Fthe BBC and became friends, who would
OL,14,Foften dine together in London.
OL,16,FHe recalls one occasion where
OL,17,Fbroadcasting giant David Dimbleby
OL,18,Fwalked in, and saw the pair.
