OL,3,CHuw Edwards 'snubbed rival' David
OL,4,CDimbleby during lunch, says ex-No 10
OL,5,Caide
OL,7,F"He waved at us from across the
OL,8,Frestaurant with a big smile on his
OL,9,Fface, and I waved back," says Guto
OL,10,FHarri, who was Boris Johnson's Head of
OL,11,FCommunications.
OL,13,F"Huw (Edwards) looked around and
OL,14,Fpretended he hadn't seen him. He said
OL,15,F'I never acknowledge him' just to make
OL,16,FDavid Dimbleby look like a fool."
OL,18,F"It was all because Huw ultimately
OL,19,Fwanted his job," Harri told S4C's
OL,20,Fcurrent affairs programme Y Byd ar
OL,21,FBedwar.
