OL,7,FHuw Edwards pleaded guilty to making
OL,8,Findecent images of children, and
OL,9,Freceived a six-months suspended jail
OL,10,Fsentence in September 2024.
OL,12,FEdwards "remembered for something
OL,13,Fawful"
OL,15,FReacting to Edwards' crimes, fellow
OL,16,FWelshman Guto Harri says he was
OL,17,F"disgusted and appalled" by the news.
