OL,3,CHuw Edwards 'snubbed rival' David
OL,4,CDimbleby during lunch, says ex-No 10
OL,5,Caide
OL,7,F"What he's helping to maintain through
OL,8,Flooking at photos like that is one of
OL,9,Fthe most filthy things anyone can
OL,10,Fthink about.
OL,12,F"We were all quite proud of him, I was
OL,13,Fquite fond of him. But he's done
OL,14,Fsomething that we're not only ashamed
OL,15,Fof but we're disgusted by."
OL,17,FHuw Edwards, 63, started his career in
OL,18,Fthe BBC in Cardiff, and had a career
OL,19,Fwhich spanned more than 40 years.
