OL,5,Caide
OL,7,FHuw Edwards did not respond to Y Byd
OL,8,Far Bedwar's request for a response,
OL,9,Fbut last year, before Edwards fronted
OL,10,Fthe King's Coronation, called David
OL,11,FDimbleby a "gold-plated Rolls-Royce
OL,12,Fbroadcaster".
OL,14,FIn a statement, the BBC said: "a Board-
OL,15,Fcommissioned independent review of the
OL,16,FBBC's workplace culture is currently
OL,17,Funderway, with a particular focus on
OL,18,Fpreventing abuse of power and ensuring
OL,19,Feveryone at the BBC conducts
OL,20,Fthemselves in line with our values."
